645
00:34:17,860 --> 00:34:18,900
Please punish her severely.

646
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:21,820
Please punish her severely.

647
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:25,260
Strip her of her fiefdom
and punish her severely.

648
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:29,620
Pingyue, you heard them
and you saw their reaction.

649
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:31,300
After causing such a big trouble,

650
00:34:31,460 --> 00:34:33,220
have you managed to find anything?

651
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:34,220
Not yet.

652
00:34:36,020 --> 00:34:37,820
However, during the investigation,

653
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:41,140
I found that all the witnesses
had been killed

654
