655
00:34:45,740 --> 00:34:46,940
I'm still investigating.

656
00:34:47,900 --> 00:34:49,620
Please give me some more time, Father.

657
00:34:49,820 --> 00:34:51,340
They are actually all dead?

658
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:52,540
It was on the outskirts of the city.

659
00:34:53,300 --> 00:34:55,940
Their corpses were left in the wild
after they were all killed.

660
00:34:57,940 --> 00:34:58,620
Father,

661
00:35:00,500 --> 00:35:01,420
if the witnesses of a case

662
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:03,620
were all killed,

663
00:35:03,820 --> 00:35:05,500
don't you think there must be
something wrong with the case?

664
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:09,740
Your Majesty, the witnesses are dead,

665
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:11,220
but the evidence is still there.

666
00:35:11,780 --> 00:35:13,220
Yang Ye's letters are verified.

667
00:35:13,660 --> 00:35:15,140
The taels of gold they took as bribes

668
00:35:15,140 --> 00:35:16,860
were also found in the Qin's mansion.

669
00:35:17,460 --> 00:35:18,340
These pieces of evidence
have been verified

670
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:21,940
by the Censorate, Ministry of Justice,
and Court of Judicial Review.

671
00:35:22,740 --> 00:35:23,900
Do you think

672
00:35:24,300 --> 00:35:27,180
that all these three organizations
are deceiving you here?

673
00:35:27,180 --> 00:35:28,900
Isn't that possible?

674
00:35:38,540 --> 00:35:39,980
When I established
the Inspectorate Office,

675
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:43,500
