is to seize power...

676
00:35:45,100 --> 00:35:47,060
and make me yield.

677
00:35:49,140 --> 00:35:50,660
You are the Minister
of the Ministry of Justice.

678
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:53,020
When faced with such a case
that's full of doubts,

679
00:35:53,260 --> 00:35:54,380
you're not thinking
about how to investigate it

680
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:55,740
to uncover the truth.

681
00:35:56,180 --> 00:35:57,700
Yet you only think
about playing with power and influence.

682
00:35:57,700 --> 00:35:58,940
You don't take people's lives
seriously at all.

683
00:35:59,180 --> 00:36:00,540
How can I not be furious?

684
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:09,100
I know very well
what you are planning to do.

685
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:10,820
But let me tell you.

686
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:14,580
The Qin Family
who you unjustly seek to destroy

687
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:17,340
are not just a few ministers

688
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:18,420
or a few living and breathing people.

689
00:36:18,740 --> 00:36:20,060
They are the walls defending our border

690
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:21,340
and the backbone of the Great Xia.

691
00:36:21,700 --> 00:36:23,220
What you seek to ruin today

692
00:36:23,340 --> 00:36:25,420
is the prosperity
and future of the Great Xia.

693
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:26,580
Therefore...

694
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,700
I will never back down.

695
00:36:39,540 --> 00:36:40,220
Go after them!

696
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:44,770
I'll bear the responsibility

697
00:36:44,770 --> 00:36:45,820
for intruding
into the Ministry of Justice.

698
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:47,380
But let me ask you this.

699
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:48,740
Do you dare to leave

700
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:50,380
the Qin Family members at my place?

701
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:51,940
Do you dare to let me investigate...

702
00:36:53,860 --> 00:36:55,140
the Qin Family's case?

703
00:37:00,940 --> 00:37:02,660
Since you claim
that the death of witnesses

704
00:37:03,580 --> 00:37:05,140
has no connection
to the Qin Family's case,

705
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:06,380
then why are you afraid
of my investigation?

706
00:37:06,460 --> 00:37:09,300
Your Majesty, it's not that I'm afraid
of Her Highness investigating the case,

707
00:37:09,740 --> 00:37:12,900
I'm just worried
that she'd continue to cause trouble.

708
00:37:14,580 --> 00:37:16,060
What if I vouch for her?

709
00:37:16,180 --> 00:37:19,500
I'm afraid you can't
restrain Princess Pingyue.

710
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:30,060
What do you want then?

711
00:37:32,300 --> 00:37:34,940
I'll definitely continue to investigate
the Qin Family's case.

712
00:37:35,660 --> 00:37:38,460
You still need to be punished.

713
00:37:38,740 --> 00:37:39,420
Your Majesty,

714
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:41,860
as the Minister
of the Ministry of Justice,

715
00:37:42,900 --> 00:37:45,580
I cannot tolerate someone
flagrantly disregarding the law.

716
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:48,940
Even if you are a princess,

717
00:37:49,940 --> 00:37:53,180
you should still abide
by the principles set by His Majesty.

718
00:37:58,500 --> 00:37:59,300
Very well.

719
00:38:00,460 --> 00:38:02,180
I will do as you wish, Mr. Xie.

720
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:04,820
Father,

721
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:07,100
I was wrong to intrude
into the Ministry of Justice.

722
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:09,620
I willingly accept the punishment
of being flogged thirty times

723
00:38:09,620 --> 00:38:11,100
and reciting scriptures
at Beiyan Pagoda for a month.

724
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:14,620
However, the Ministry of Justices
failed in their duties

725
00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:16,500
by not adequately protecting
key witnesses,

726
00:38:16,500 --> 00:38:19,140
indirectly leading to their deaths.

727
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:20,860
This is their first wrongdoing.

728
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:23,300
Father appointed me to take charge
of the Inspectorate Office,

729
00:38:23,860 --> 00:38:26,620
but the Ministry of Justices
refused to follow imperial orders,

730
00:38:26,740 --> 00:38:28,340
did not fully cooperate
with the investigation.

731
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:30,020
Instead, under the guise of regulations,

732
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:31,660
they obstructed me in every way,

733
00:38:32,340 --> 00:38:33,700
disregarding Father's authority.

734
00:38:34,540 --> 00:38:35,580
This is their second wrongdoing.

735
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:36,660
Your Majesty...

736
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,770
Now, upon learning of the deaths

737
00:38:37,770 --> 00:38:39,340
of the witnesses
and the doubts in this case,

738
00:38:39,340 --> 00:38:41,220
they have neglected their duties,
refusing to investigate thoroughly.

739
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:42,900
This is their third wrongdoing.

740
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:44,140
That's completely nonsense.

741
00:38:44,140 --> 00:38:46,220
Mr. Xie is the Minister
of the Ministry of Justice

742
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:47,100
and he's in charge of it.

743
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:49,980
Yet now, the Ministry of Justice
is plagued with numerous problems.

744
00:38:50,140 --> 00:38:52,020
Mr. Xie has to be held accountable.

745
00:38:52,460 --> 00:38:53,740
I voluntarily accept my punishment.

746
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:57,100
However, cleaning up the Ministry
of Justice is imperative.

747
00:38:58,100 --> 00:38:59,220
Although these three wrongdoings

748
00:38:59,220 --> 00:39:00,860
are mainly shown
through the Qin Family's case,

749
00:39:01,100 --> 00:39:02,340
the overall situation
can still be deduced.

750
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:04,660
The Ministry of Justice's usual ways
of handling cases

751
00:39:04,660 --> 00:39:06,220
are indeed harmful to the state.

752
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:07,980
Father,
please thoroughly investigate them

753
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:09,140
without any leniency.

754
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:13,620
My niece is different now.

755
00:39:15,380 --> 00:39:16,740
What Her Highness said is reasonable.

756
00:39:16,860 --> 00:39:18,460
I request you to thoroughly investigate

757
00:39:18,460 --> 00:39:19,460
those in the Ministry of Justice,
Your Majesty.

758
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:22,720
- Please punish
- Please punish

759
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:24,580
- the Ministry of Justice severely.
- the Ministry of Justice severely.

760
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:25,700
Father.

761
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:27,900
Since I've already

762
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:29,540
intervened in the Qin Family's case,

763
00:39:29,820 --> 00:39:30,860
I will not quit so easily.

764
00:39:31,140 --> 00:39:33,260
Please grant me another twenty days.

765
00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:36,140
Your Majesty, please don't...

766
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:37,140
If nothing is uncovered...

767
00:39:39,540 --> 00:39:40,860
after twenty days,

768
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:45,420
it will prove that there is no injustice
in the Qin Family's case

769
00:39:45,780 --> 00:39:47,100
and that I have been unreasonable.

770
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:49,220
I shall willingly accept my punishment

771
00:39:50,540 --> 00:39:53,060
of being expelled from the capital
and return to my fiefdom.

772
00:39:55,940 --> 00:39:56,900
I'll never enter the capital again.

773
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:04,620
Your request is granted.

774
00:41:03,220 --> 00:41:03,940
Your Highness.

