a different person.

786
00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:49,260
It seems Pei Wenxuan
has had a significant influence on her.

787
00:41:49,700 --> 00:41:50,620
It seems

788
00:41:51,460 --> 00:41:52,940
to be the only explanation.

789
00:41:55,180 --> 00:41:56,900
You should go to Beiyan Pagoda
and tell her

790
00:41:57,820 --> 00:41:59,380
